{"body": "Thanks for the ideas.  @yfeldblum that solution works, but it feels unnatural to me to put the implementation of what are NumberHelper methods injected to all strings.  Yes, we want to support translating a string that is numberish into a phone number, but for most strings these methods wont be relevant.  It would surprise me if I looked at the methods for \"banana\" and found a \"to_phone\" method.\n", "url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rails/rails/issues/comments/5726887", "created_at": "2012-05-15T20:45:23Z", "html_url": "https://github.com/rails/rails/pull/6315#issuecomment-5726887", "updated_at": "2012-05-15T20:45:23Z", "repo": "rails", "issue_id": 6315, "user": {"following_url": "https://api.github.com/users/amutz/following{/other_user}", "events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/amutz/events{/privacy}", "organizations_url": "https://api.github.com/users/amutz/orgs", "url": "https://api.github.com/users/amutz", "gists_url": "https://api.github.com/users/amutz/gists{/gist_id}", "html_url": "https://github.com/amutz", "subscriptions_url": "https://api.github.com/users/amutz/subscriptions", "avatar_url": "https://2.gravatar.com/avatar/aed424af11b9f92cca6c051f75f013b7?d=https%3A%2F%2Fidenticons.github.com%2F77d85e54bebbad4c976bf8fc0923c567.png", "repos_url": "https://api.github.com/users/amutz/repos", "received_events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/amutz/received_events", "gravatar_id": "aed424af11b9f92cca6c051f75f013b7", "starred_url": "https://api.github.com/users/amutz/starred{/owner}{/repo}", "login": "amutz", "type": "User", "id": 919763, "followers_url": "https://api.github.com/users/amutz/followers"}, "owner": "rails", "_id": {"$oid": "523e6611bd354364b900fb6c"}, "id": 5726887, "issue_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rails/rails/issues/6315"}
